      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Information_NetZeroTransactions",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve and display information related to \"Net Zero Transactions\" from a utility company's database. It performs three main queries to extract data from different tables within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ConEd",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema, focusing on transactions that have a net-zero impact. The procedure does not take any input parameters and outputs three result sets, each providing different perspectives on net-zero transactions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Low"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this stored procedure is low. It involves straightforward SQL SELECT statements with simple filtering and ordering operations. There are no complex joins, subqueries, or conditional logic that would increase its complexity."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This stored procedure does not have any input parameters. It operates on predefined tables and extracts data based on the existing records in those tables."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
